{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja monitor template for Spectra LS P6-S02 control-center settings-contract validation and bounded closeout gating. #}
{# Version: 2026.04.21.1 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-21 #}

{# =========================
  P6-S02 Control-Center Settings Monitor (read-only-first)
  Purpose: classify settings-contract readiness and closeout posture for options-flow + `spectra_ls.set_control_center_settings` surfaces.
  Usage:
    1) Apply one bounded settings update (integration options or service patch).
    2) Paste/run in Developer Tools -> Template.
    3) Capture output in checklist evidence block.
  ========================= #}

{% set s_target_primary = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_target_fallback = 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set primary_has_attrs = state_attr(s_target_primary, 'route_trace') is not none or state_attr(s_target_primary, 'captured_at') is not none %}
{% set fallback_has_attrs = state_attr(s_target_fallback, 'route_trace') is not none or state_attr(s_target_fallback, 'captured_at') is not none %}
{% set s_target = s_target_primary if primary_has_attrs else (s_target_fallback if fallback_has_attrs else s_target_primary) %}

{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target, 'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set contract = state_attr(s_target, 'contract_validation') or {} %}
{% set write_controls = state_attr(s_target, 'write_controls') or {} %}
{% set control_validation = state_attr(s_target, 'control_center_validation') or {} %}
{% set unresolved = state_attr(s_target, 'unresolved_sources') or [] %}
{% set mismatches = state_attr(s_target, 'mismatches') or [] %}

{% set authority_mode = write_controls.authority_mode if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.authority_mode is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set control_settings = write_controls.control_center_settings if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.control_center_settings is defined and write_controls.control_center_settings is mapping else {} %}
{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set contract_valid = contract.valid if contract is mapping and contract.valid is defined else false %}
{% set missing_required = contract.missing_required if contract is mapping and contract.missing_required is defined else [] %}
{% set unresolved_required = contract.unresolved_required if contract is mapping and contract.unresolved_required is defined else [] %}

{% set schema_version = control_validation.schema_version if control_validation is mapping and control_validation.schema_version is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set settings_present = control_validation.settings_present if control_validation is mapping and control_validation.settings_present is defined else false %}
{% set ready_for_customization = control_validation.ready_for_customization if control_validation is mapping and control_validation.ready_for_customization is defined else false %}
{% set required_keys = control_validation.required_keys if control_validation is mapping and control_validation.required_keys is defined else [] %}
{% set unresolved_scene_bindings = control_validation.unresolved_scene_bindings if control_validation is mapping and control_validation.unresolved_scene_bindings is defined else [] %}
{% set read_only_mode = control_settings.read_only_mode if control_settings is mapping and control_settings.read_only_mode is defined else true %}

{% set captured_at = state_attr(s_target, 'captured_at') | default('', true) %}
{% set captured_ts = as_timestamp(captured_at) if captured_at not in ['', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', none] else none %}
{% set age_s = (as_timestamp(now()) - captured_ts) if captured_ts is not none else none %}
{% set snapshot_fresh = age_s is not none and age_s <= 300 %}

{# --- Operator-confirmed P6 governance gates (set true/false before capture) --- #}
{% set p6_s01_active = true %}
{% set read_only_first_posture = true %}
{% set rollback_posture_documented = true %}
{% set compatibility_posture_documented = true %}

{% set runtime_baseline_gate_pass = authority_mode == 'legacy' and contract_valid and (missing_required | length) == 0 and (unresolved_required | length) == 0 and (unresolved | length) == 0 and (mismatches | length) == 0 and snapshot_fresh %}
{% set settings_surface_gate_pass = settings_present and ready_for_customization and (required_keys | length) > 0 and schema_version != 'missing' %}
{% set read_only_gate_pass = (read_only_mode == true and read_only_first_posture) or (read_only_mode == false) %}
{% set governance_gate_pass = p6_s01_active and compatibility_posture_documented and rollback_posture_documented %}

{% set gate_pass_count = (1 if runtime_baseline_gate_pass else 0)
  + (1 if settings_surface_gate_pass else 0)
  + (1 if read_only_gate_pass else 0)
  + (1 if governance_gate_pass else 0) %}

{% set status = 'PASS' %}
{% if not runtime_baseline_gate_pass or not settings_surface_gate_pass %}
  {% set status = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif not read_only_gate_pass or not governance_gate_pass %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

{% set p6_readiness = 'NOT_READY' %}
{% if status == 'PASS' and gate_pass_count == 4 %}
  {% set p6_readiness = 'READY' %}
{% elif status == 'FAIL' %}
  {% set p6_readiness = 'BLOCKED' %}
{% else %}
  {% set p6_readiness = 'CAUTION' %}
{% endif %}

### P6-S02 Control-Center Settings Monitor (`spectra_ls`)
- Status: **{{ status }}**
- P6-S02 readiness: **{{ p6_readiness }}**
- Gate score: **{{ gate_pass_count }}/4**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**

### Runtime + settings gates (live)
- Runtime baseline gate (legacy + clean contract/parity + fresh): **{{ runtime_baseline_gate_pass }}**
- Settings-surface gate (schema + required keys + customization ready): **{{ settings_surface_gate_pass }}**
- Read-only-first posture gate: **{{ read_only_gate_pass }}**
- Governance gate (P6-S01 active + compatibility/rollback posture): **{{ governance_gate_pass }}**

### Settings snapshot
- `authority_mode`: **{{ authority_mode }}**
- `route_trace.decision`: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `control_center_validation.schema_version`: **{{ schema_version }}**
- `settings_present`: **{{ settings_present }}**
- `ready_for_customization`: **{{ ready_for_customization }}**
- `required_keys`: **{{ required_keys | length }}**
- `unresolved_scene_bindings`: **{{ unresolved_scene_bindings | length }}**
- `read_only_mode`: **{{ read_only_mode }}**
- `contract_validation.missing_required`: **{{ missing_required | length }}**
- `contract_validation.unresolved_required`: **{{ unresolved_required | length }}**
- `unresolved_sources`: **{{ unresolved | length }}**
- `mismatches`: **{{ mismatches | length }}**
- Freshness (`captured_at<=300s`): **{{ snapshot_fresh }}** (age_s={{ (age_s | round(1)) if age_s is not none else 'n/a' }})

### Quick interpretation
{% if p6_readiness == 'READY' %}
- P6-S02 settings-contract lane is healthy for bounded validation evidence and closeout tracking.
{% elif p6_readiness == 'CAUTION' %}
- P6-S02 is partially healthy; resolve read-only/governance posture gaps before closeout.
{% elif p6_readiness == 'BLOCKED' %}
- P6-S02 is blocked by baseline or settings-surface failure; resolve before proceeding.
{% else %}
- P6-S02 readiness is not established yet; gather missing evidence and re-run.
{% endif %}

### Suggested refresh actions
- Apply one bounded settings update via integration options or `spectra_ls.set_control_center_settings`.
- Keep `authority_mode=legacy` baseline unless an explicitly approved bounded slice changes ownership.
- Attach this output to `p6_s02_control_center_settings_checklist.md` evidence record.
